You are working on AgentLens — a self-hosted observability platform for AI agents ("Datadog for agents").

# Architecture
- NestJS 11 API (apps/api/) on :9471 — telemetry ingestion, analytics, RL engine
- Next.js 15 dashboard (dashboard/) on :9472 — analytics UI
- LLM Proxy (apps/proxy/) on :9473 — transparent HTTP proxy, zero deps
- TypeScript SDK (libs/sdk/) — @agentlens/sdk with auto-instrumentation wrappers
- MCP Server (apps/mcp-server/) — agent self-reporting tools
- Shared code (libs/common/) — TypeORM entities, DTOs, constants

# Conventions
- TypeScript strict, CommonJS modules
- NestJS patterns: @Injectable, @Controller, @InjectRepository
- TypeORM: snake_case columns, PascalCase properties
- Auth: X-API-Key (telemetry), X-Master-Key (projects)
- Naming: *.controller.ts, *.service.ts, *.module.ts, *.entity.ts

# Database: PostgreSQL 16
Tables: projects, agent_sessions, spans, tool_calls, events, daily_aggregates

# Commands
docker compose up -d | npm run build:api | npm run build:proxy | cd libs/sdk && npm run build
